@DATABASE "Jack The Nipper 2"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - J - Jack The Nipper 2"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - J
                   ====================================

                             Jack The Nipper 2
                             =================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43251,0)"}          43251,0
@{"Infinite Ammo " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(38306,0)"}          38306,0
@{"Lives = x     " rxs "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(34631,255)"}          34631,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Immunity 1    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(34426,0)"}          34426,0
@{"Immunity 2    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43203,201) ZXAMPoke(41222,205) ZXAMPoke(41229,205) ZXAMPoke(41330,205) ZXAMPoke(41444,205) ZXAMPoke(41576,205) ZXAMPoke(41696,205) ZXAMPoke(41763,205) ZXAMPoke(41797,205) ZXAMPoke(42314,205)"}          43203,201:41222,205:41229,205:41330,205:41444,205:
                         41576,205:41696,205:41763,205:41797,205:42314,205
                         (Phew!!!)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         The "Infinite Ammo" gives you infinite coconuts,
                         or whatever weapon you have.

                         "Immunity 1" gives you infinite "shields" after
                         you die.

                         "Immunity 2" gives you complete immunity.

                         I wouldn't use the Immunity 2 POKE if I were you
                         as you get completely stuck if you fall in the water,
                         and you have to quit the game :(

                         The "Lives = x" POKE is mine. Someone had already
                         done the other two...

                         Rastan.
@endnode
